{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"main_7_level_main_07-16_beg","storyGroup":"main_7","storySort":17,"storyDependence":"main_7_level_main_07-15_end","storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":"7-18","storyName":"爱国者之死","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"爱国者如同一座大山拦在罗德岛一行面前，要将其跨过唯有战胜他一途。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"obt/main/level_main_07-16_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"main_07-16","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":15,"next":17,"characters":["凯尔希","爱国者","盾卫","阿米娅","萨卡兹雇佣兵","罗德岛近卫干员？","迷迭香","罗德岛干员"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"dialog","id":2},{"type":"character","id":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/47/Avg_bg_bg_chercen_1.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":6},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$exciting_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_exciting02_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":8},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_025_1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":9},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":10},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":11},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"博卓卡斯替，久违了。","id":12,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_025_1","id":13},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"——","id":14,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"凯尔希，女勋爵？","id":15,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"你为什么......没有变老？","id":16,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"盾卫。游击队，待命。不必全来这里。","id":17,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058","id":18},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"是。","id":19,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_025_1","id":20},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"勋爵。","id":21,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_025_1","focus":"1","id":22},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"你的发音习惯......你的病变器官在喉咙处？","id":23,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_025_1","focus":"2","id":24},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"不。只是，时日长久，变成这样。我没法，再顺利，说话。","id":25,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"勋爵......我甚至没想过，能再见你。","id":26,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我依稀记得，我与族人离去时，你与那位殿下，并未阻拦我们。","id":27,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_025_1","focus":"1","id":28},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"那是很久、很久之前的事了。","id":29,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_025_1","focus":"2","id":30},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"那时我，年轻气盛，现在看，全是一时冲动。我误会了，殿下的意思。","id":31,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_025_1","focus":"1","id":32},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......你还肯叫她殿下。","id":33,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_025_1","focus":"2","id":34},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"君王，就是君王。","id":35,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"即使我走时，她仍不是；即使现在，她已身殁。","id":36,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#4","id":37},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......","id":38,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ed/Avg_char_002_amiya_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_025_1","focus":"1","id":39},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"你依然能将卡兹戴尔的君主与乌萨斯的皇帝清楚分开。","id":40,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_025_1","focus":"2","id":41},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我有分寸。战争还无法，搅乱我思绪。我事奉的人，都已逝去。","id":42,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我已将乌萨斯，也看作祖国。我的陛下，已葬身乌萨斯，漫大土地。","id":43,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"......太久远了，勋爵。我们离去时......","id":44,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"那时我族还未，凋零至斯，却也只，苟延一息。","id":45,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"但你......没有变。岁月，没有改变你。","id":46,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_025_1","focus":"1","id":47},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"不，岁月不可避免地改变了我们，博卓卡斯替。我已不再是过去的我。","id":48,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"博卓卡斯替......你为何离开卡兹戴尔？","id":49,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_025_1","focus":"2","id":50},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我离开的缘由，大概，会令人耻笑。","id":51,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我离开，卡兹戴尔，是因厌恶杀人。","id":52,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"......但穷我一生，我都在杀人。","id":53,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_025_1","focus":"1","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"经历没有左右你的意志，你血管里依然流着不会止歇的热血。你并不可笑，你值得尊敬。","id":55,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_025_1","focus":"2","id":56},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"言过，勋爵。杀人这事，我不可能回避。我确实，杀了无数人。","id":57,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"勋爵，你可知，我现在称号，从哪里来？","id":58,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_025_1","focus":"1","id":59},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"你的追随者认为你是真正为乌萨斯奋斗的战士。你为了乌萨斯的未来，与不公，奴役，血腥和压迫战斗。","id":60,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"你会这么认为吗？","id":61,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_025_1","id":62},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"（摇头）","id":63,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"即使斗争，属于必然，冠上名头，还是令人厌烦。","id":64,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"为了许多人，我们发动战争。可是战争，终归杀人。","id":65,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"战争结束，如果，战争真的结束，我们都该，死。","id":66,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":67},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"可战争永不结束。","id":68,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_025_1","id":69},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"可我会死。","id":70,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"只是，我要死得，有价值。我要看到，感染者和，乌萨斯的，另一种未来。","id":71,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我曾多次，向同胞打听，卡兹戴尔。您与殿下，共事多年。她信任你。","id":72,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"既然，她信任你，那我也可，信任你。","id":73,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"你领罗德岛，来到此处，非为流血之事。","id":74,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"......即使你身后，那两人，已经沾上，我女儿，死亡的气息。","id":75,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#2","id":76},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"——！","id":77,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/fc/Avg_char_003_kalts_2.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":78},{"type":"character","id":79},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"81","text":"我？和......阿米娅......"}},"values":[],"id":80},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":81,"end":83},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#4","id":82},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"爱国者先生......","id":83,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ed/Avg_char_002_amiya_4.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":84},{"type":"character","id":85},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"87","text":"霜星她为了考验我们——"}},"values":[],"id":86},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":87,"end":96},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_025_1","id":88},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"不。不要再说。","id":89,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_025_1","focus":"1","id":90},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"你要报复罗德岛吗，爱国者？","id":91,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_025_1","focus":"2","id":92},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"不，勋爵。我不准备，报复。","id":93,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我为何，要为她的作为，报复别人？","id":94,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"那路，是她自己所选。无论那路，会通向哪里。","id":95,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"character","id":96,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":97},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"99","text":"您的女儿全力与我们战斗！"},"2":{"id":"99","text":"她很强。"},"3":{"id":"99","text":"霜星的意志十分坚定。"}},"values":[],"id":98},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":99},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"101","text":"她也认可了我们。"}},"values":[],"id":100},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":101},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_025_1","id":102},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"住嘴。","id":103,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"105","text":"......什么？"}},"values":[],"id":104},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":105},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#4","id":106},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......爱国者先生？","id":107,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ed/Avg_char_002_amiya_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_025_1","id":108},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"她，这点年纪，只懂得，盲目托付。","id":109,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"事实上，我们相信的，最后都暴露。只是些，慈眉善目的，恶徒。","id":110,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"112","text":"你......！"}},"values":[],"id":111},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":112},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#4","name2":"avg_npc_025_1","focus":"1","id":113},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"爱国者先生！可是霜星小姐，把她的生命，她的法术......全都，全都......","id":114,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ed/Avg_char_002_amiya_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"霜星小姐是真的将她所有的一切都释放了出来，只为了证明她自己，她的怒火，她的理想......","id":115,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ed/Avg_char_002_amiya_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"她的生命是有价值的！","id":116,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ed/Avg_char_002_amiya_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#4","name2":"avg_npc_025_1","focus":"2","id":117},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"够了。你不配，这么说。","id":118,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#4","name2":"avg_npc_025_1","focus":"1","id":119},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"啊......","id":120,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ed/Avg_char_002_amiya_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":121},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"（阿米娅，不。先别说了。）","id":122,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_025_1","id":123},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"你又懂什么？","id":124,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"如果我的女儿，没有病入膏肓，她杀你们，轻而易举，如同用镰刀，收割麦穗。","id":125,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"你们身上，发生什么，我不感兴趣。","id":126,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我对，这些，没有兴趣。什么也，证明不了。","id":127,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"129","text":"现在的塔露拉，正让核心城撞向龙门！"}},"values":[],"id":128},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":129},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"是不是，还宣扬这是，乌萨斯领土？","id":130,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"132","text":"你怎么会知道？！"},"2":{"id":"132","text":"......"},"3":{"id":"132","text":"看来不用我们告诉你。"}},"values":[],"id":131},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":132},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1","name2":"avg_npc_025_1","focus":"1","id":133},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"爱国者......怎么......那为什么......","id":134,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_char_002_amiya_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_025_1","id":135},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"阴谋家的手段，层出不穷。阴谋家的想法，大同小异。","id":136,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"但我不可能，让出道路。整合运动，不能自毁。","id":137,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我不会，再成为叛徒。一旦我背叛，全部感染者，所有斗争，都失去正当，都将败亡。","id":138,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"即使塔露拉，已经错乱......","id":139,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我该如何，向感染者说，他们的领袖，是疯子，或是叛徒？","id":140,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"如何说，她现在错误，过去却正确？如何说，她，你们之前追随，现在，要把她处决？","id":141,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我不会，让整合运动，被记述成，“感染者内乱，而后消灭”。我不会。","id":142,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_025_1","focus":"1","id":143},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"但整合运动将先支撑不住自身重量。何况塔露拉已经暗中把整合运动搅动得支离破碎。","id":144,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_025_1","focus":"2","id":145},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"您说的都对，凯尔希女爵。","id":146,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"所以您在这里。","id":147,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我做好了，面对各种敌人，所有准备。","id":148,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"却没想到，我的敌人，最终还是，感染者。","id":149,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_025_1","focus":"1","id":150},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......你真要这么选？","id":151,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"博卓卡斯替......你可以选择不死的。","id":152,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_025_1","id":153},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"选择？我的选择，只有一种。","id":154,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我杀死你们。","id":155,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#4","id":156},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"爱国者，我们之间不应该产生无谓的牺牲！和霜星小姐不一样，这次战斗，无论给谁带来损失，都只是中了敌人圈套！","id":157,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ed/Avg_char_002_amiya_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_025_1","id":158},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"错了。","id":159,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"卡特斯人，这是，战争。","id":160,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"你要我停手。我为什么要，停手？","id":161,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我已经打过，太多的仗。","id":162,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"身为，乌萨斯的，温迪戈时......蛮族。剥皮者，拆骨食肉，恶毒的畜群，我们净化。","id":163,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"怪物。生长扭曲，腥臭长肢，百眼，千指，我们屠戮。","id":164,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"战士。维多利亚，蒸汽的甲胄，卡西米尔，银枪的天马，拉特兰城，教宗的铳骑，我们，统统战胜。","id":165,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"但我们，战胜不了自己。战胜不了，帝国的贪欲。战胜不了，同胞的死。","id":166,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我们温迪戈，在萨卡兹中，离死亡最近。","id":167,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"你们沾上了，我女儿的死。","id":168,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"这大地上，有比死亡，更糟的命运。","id":169,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我为何该停手？谁胆敢考验我，作为人的道德？","id":170,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我被认定是，正直，所以我该，坦然接受？","id":171,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我被命运，当作弱者，所以我该，逆来顺受？！我被当做强者，我就该，全部承担？","id":172,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"背叛者，反抗者，屠杀者，坚守者......","id":173,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"所有称号，都如“爱国者”般，只是，战场的零碎。","id":174,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"罗德岛......","id":175,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"你们杀了她。我也将杀了你们。","id":176,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我并非，寻求报复；我毫无，复仇之心。","id":177,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我女儿只是，放弃了斗争。","id":178,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"180","text":"不对！"},"2":{"id":"180","text":"......"},"3":{"id":"180","text":"不是你说的那样，老先生。"}},"values":[],"id":179},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":180,"end":228},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"如果她没放弃，她怎会，耗尽生命，容你们活着？！","id":181,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我，不会。","id":182,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我只相信，双目所见。我只相信，一手所握。","id":183,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我不因为，我的女儿，而与你们敌对。","id":184,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"......但我厌恨命运。","id":185,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我要将它，击坠，揉碎，磨至尘灰。","id":186,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"如果命运，让你们，逼我转向。","id":187,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我宁可，永不回头。","id":188,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058","id":189},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"......大尉！你真的要......","id":190,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_025_1","id":191},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"有谁觉得，我不荣誉，现在就，向我挑战。","id":192,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"但你们如果，觉得生命可贵......我们，在此分别。","id":193,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我不想你们，愚昧地死。 我胜过太多次。这个道理，我太清楚。","id":194,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#4","id":195},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"难道......","id":196,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ed/Avg_char_002_amiya_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_025_1","focus":"1","id":197},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"博卓卡斯替，你可以活下去，不要做傻事。","id":198,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_025_1","focus":"2","id":199},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"勋爵，你也尝过，失去的滋味。","id":200,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"既然尝过，你难道能，无动于衷？","id":201,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_025_1","focus":"1","id":202},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"——你——","id":203,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_025_1","focus":"2","id":204},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我的血脉，不再效忠她了。是的，现下我的祖国......是乌萨斯。","id":205,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"但她死时，我们都听见......听见那声，长久叹息。","id":206,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_025_1","focus":"1","id":207},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......","id":208,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"你居然能感受到......","id":209,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"那是蕴含她法术的能量脉冲扩散至整片大地的萨卡兹体内的一刻。","id":210,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"那只是一个瞬间，你能感受到，这说明你的血脉......足够古老。","id":211,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_025_1","focus":"2","id":212},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"古老到已经，举目无亲。","id":213,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我未曾想过，我生于，卡兹戴尔，却未感染，矿石病；等我年岁已老，却尝到，感染滋味。","id":214,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"这正确吗？","id":215,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我们都知道，勋爵。我们都知道，这大地上的事，不因其正确，才会发生。","id":216,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"事实上，这大地上的事，大多一错再错。","id":217,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"士兵们说，我知错能改；事实上，我积重难返，无法回头。","id":218,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"你是为，已经失去的，战斗至今吗，勋爵？","id":219,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我认为，你不是。","id":220,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"你是因为，有所失，才决定，不要再失去。","id":221,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"avg_npc_025_1","focus":"1","id":222},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......","id":223,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_025_1","id":224},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我女儿，已经过世。","id":225,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"——我不会，为她的死而战。我会为，还活着的，所有感染者，战斗到最后。","id":226,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"整合运动，不能失败。","id":227,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"整合运动必须，解放所有感染者。","id":228,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":229},{"type":"character","id":230},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":231},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":232},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_053","id":233},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵","text":"你是要帮他和他的士兵通风报信？","id":234,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵","text":"等碰面了，你想说什么呢？","id":235,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_053","name2":"avg_npc_059","focus":"2","id":236},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛近卫干员？","text":"......你们想要陷害游击队。你们想......想煽动其他乌萨斯感染者，害死他们。","id":237,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c5/Avg_avg_npc_059.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛近卫干员？","text":"你知道他们不会对平民出手。","id":238,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c5/Avg_avg_npc_059.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_053","name2":"avg_npc_059","focus":"1","id":239},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵","text":"仇恨是最强的武器，杀谁，谁就死。","id":240,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_059","id":241},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛近卫干员？","text":"但他是不会死的。","id":242,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c5/Avg_avg_npc_059.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛近卫干员？","text":"他是爱国者......我听到的所有传说最后都融成一处，我看过他的铠甲，我看到过他挥舞武器。","id":243,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c5/Avg_avg_npc_059.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛近卫干员？","text":"他绝对不会死！他和他的队伍，才是整合运动最坚强的卫士！","id":244,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c5/Avg_avg_npc_059.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛近卫干员？","text":"你们想害感染者，你们这些魔族人从来不在乎别人死活，但他在乎！","id":245,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c5/Avg_avg_npc_059.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛近卫干员？","text":"他是乌萨斯人......是萨卡兹，还是感染者！可他绝不会为其中一个身份而做出邪恶的事情！","id":246,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c5/Avg_avg_npc_059.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛近卫干员？","text":"所以，他既不只是乌萨斯人，也不光是萨卡兹，更不是个纯粹的感染者。他是爱国者，只有他才是爱国者。","id":247,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c5/Avg_avg_npc_059.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛近卫干员？","text":"他会击倒你们，防住你们的攻击，唾弃你们的侮蔑，重整感染者，清扫他们的仇恨......","id":248,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c5/Avg_avg_npc_059.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛近卫干员？","text":"他是爱国者，他不会死。","id":249,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c5/Avg_avg_npc_059.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛近卫干员？","text":"而你们不过是些卑劣的、阴谋家豢养的蛆。","id":250,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c5/Avg_avg_npc_059.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_053","id":251},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵","text":"......","id":252,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵","text":"你是知道自己活不下去，才这么说的。","id":253,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵","text":"你的预感很对。","id":254,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹雇佣兵","text":"爱国者也许坚固，但你脆弱得很。你会死。","id":255,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":256},{"type":"dialog","id":257},{"type":"character","id":258},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":259},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$bat_patriot_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d2d0/m_bat_patriot_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":260,"musicid":1},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":261},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_025_1","id":262},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"所以我，不会让路。","id":263,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"你想通过，中央区，你只能杀死我。","id":264,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"否则，游击队会展开，无穷的追杀，而我会在这里，直接扼死你们。","id":265,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"你们会，被我杀死。","id":266,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"你们的价值，只有在，杀死我后，才得彰显。否则，你们只是一支，入侵者。","id":267,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"269","text":"你有问题吧？！"},"2":{"id":"269","text":"......不可理喻。"},"3":{"id":"269","text":"我有点不能理解你在说什么了。"}},"values":[],"id":268},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":269},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"当然，我根本不相信，你们有什么，价值。","id":270,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我不知道，你们如何，成功抵御，我族巫术；但你们，抵御不住，乌萨斯的战术。","id":271,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"273","text":"你就那么恨我们吗？"}},"values":[],"id":272},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":273,"end":313},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我没有，憎恨谁。","id":274,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我只是，不相信你们。我不可能，相信。","id":275,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"即使是你，勋爵，是你带领......","id":276,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":277},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"你也不会认同我们。","id":278,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_025_1","id":279},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我不相信，命运安排的，所有巧合。","id":280,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"战争。","id":281,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"战争，不问对错。","id":282,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"不是，受难者，不是，受压迫者，不是，遭奴役者。战场下，有，战场上，没有这些。","id":283,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"走上战场，当有准备。","id":284,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"谁死，谁错。","id":285,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","id":286},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"没......没办法理解这个人......！","id":287,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_012","id":288},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"他在说什么......我们为什么要战斗？","id":289,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_npc_012.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_025_1","id":290},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"你们不战斗，会被碾碎。","id":291,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"你们反抗，也会被碾碎。","id":292,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"除非你们胜过我。","id":293,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"如果命运，站在我身侧，我先杀你们，再去屠戮它，让它没有机会，再嘲笑谁。","id":294,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"如果命运，站在你们身后。","id":295,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我就只会，向前走。我会进军。","id":296,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","id":297},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......","id":298,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"所有干员，立刻，退后！","id":299,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_025_1","id":300},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我将要迈步。","id":301,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#3","id":302},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我们的敌人是整合运动的指挥官之一，代号“爱国者”的感染者！","id":303,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/14/Avg_char_003_kalts_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"他的铠甲，他的力量，他的身躯，将会超过你们对一个战士的所有想象。","id":304,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/14/Avg_char_003_kalts_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"源石可能已经取代了他许多生理机能，所谓喉咙处的源石......是他高结晶率身体的副产物。","id":305,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/14/Avg_char_003_kalts_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"这是我们从情报中分析出的最结论性的结果。","id":306,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/14/Avg_char_003_kalts_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我有理由相信，普通的致死性伤口根本无法对他造成实质性伤害，因为源石只会不断生长，替代他的生理组织！","id":307,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/14/Avg_char_003_kalts_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"温迪戈的身体本就拥有极强的新陈代谢和修复能力，而现在，我们并不知道感染给他带来的是病痛还是良性的变异。","id":308,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/14/Avg_char_003_kalts_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"但不论他有多么强韧，我们也必须击杀他。","id":309,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/14/Avg_char_003_kalts_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"只有击杀他，我们才能穿过中央区，走向舰桥，去阻止敌人对整合运动的利用！","id":310,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/14/Avg_char_003_kalts_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"他的卫队尚对他的举动感到混乱，现在就是最后的机会。","id":311,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/14/Avg_char_003_kalts_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#4","id":312},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"医生......","id":313,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ed/Avg_char_002_amiya_4.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":314},{"type":"character","id":315},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"317","text":"咋回事？"},"2":{"id":"317","text":"......为什么？"},"3":{"id":"317","text":"事情怎么变成这样？"}},"values":[],"id":316},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":317,"end":340},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#3","id":318},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......我们只是他道路上的一支选择。我们事业的建树，对他来说并无意义。","id":319,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/14/Avg_char_003_kalts_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"对他而言，我们可能和“现在立刻去杀死塔露拉”是一回事。只不过后者在他眼里更有重量，更值得研究。","id":320,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/14/Avg_char_003_kalts_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"简单地说，他看不起我们。","id":321,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/14/Avg_char_003_kalts_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#4","id":322},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"即使医生你在这也......","id":323,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ed/Avg_char_002_amiya_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#3","id":324},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"即使是帝国皇帝也不能教他低头，何况是我。","id":325,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/14/Avg_char_003_kalts_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我们要用他自己的死......让他睁眼，让他侧目，让他注意到我们所做的一切确实有力，让他意识到我们比他更强。","id":326,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/14/Avg_char_003_kalts_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"但他本人根本不可能......改变。其他的一切，你们看重的一切，对他来说太脆弱了，脆弱到承受不住他的重压。","id":327,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/14/Avg_char_003_kalts_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"阿撒兹勒的赫拉格错估了这个萨卡兹的品性。","id":328,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/14/Avg_char_003_kalts_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......博卓卡斯替再高尚、背负再多，他也首先是无可匹敌的战士。","id":329,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/14/Avg_char_003_kalts_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"霜星信任你们，所以将生命最后一点时间交予你们......但爱国者不是。","id":330,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/14/Avg_char_003_kalts_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"爱国者全然不信。他只相信自己。","id":331,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/14/Avg_char_003_kalts_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"（......哪怕表面如此。）","id":332,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/14/Avg_char_003_kalts_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"准备战斗。只有战斗能决定结果。","id":333,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/14/Avg_char_003_kalts_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"——只有战争能杀死他。","id":334,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/14/Avg_char_003_kalts_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_025_1","id":335},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"明智的决定，勋爵。","id":336,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"游击队，即将重整。","id":337,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"你们的时间，只剩下几分钟。","id":338,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我不说，更多话。","id":339,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我不寻求，理解。我只，打赢战争。","id":340,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":341},{"type":"character","id":342},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.2","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":343},{"type":"text","text":"永远无法被理解，被称作怪物的可怖战士屹立在场。","id":344},{"type":"text","text":"但是，你想起，身边也有个能理解所有、同样被称作怪物的战士......","id":345},{"type":"text","text":"阿米娅握紧了你的手。","id":346},{"type":"character","id":347},{"type":"dialog","id":348},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":349},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_025_1","id":350},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"罗德岛，我将进军。","id":351,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3f/Avg_avg_npc_025_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":352},{"type":"blocker","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":353},{"type":"image","id":354}],"characters":["凯尔希","爱国者","盾卫","阿米娅","萨卡兹雇佣兵","罗德岛近卫干员？","迷迭香","罗德岛干员"]}